{"tid":150142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國強制實施亞裔學生再細分，華裔家長不滿","createTime":"2017-03-09T20:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T05:08:33.000Z","uid":22675,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d98a773314ecb8e6e3e74c164357a247a158afa","tid":150142,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T20:25:56.000Z","msg":"加州爾灣市有華裔家長發現新生註冊表格上，竟要求亞裔人士必須細分自己是華裔還是日、韓等其他亞洲族裔，引起華裔家長的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n特別的是，白人、非裔、拉丁裔等都是有大項選擇，唯獨亞裔部分，被細分成了華裔、日裔、韓裔、越裔、柬埔寨裔、菲律賓裔、其他太平洋島嶼裔(Other Pacific Islander)等多種選項，並且選項中還註明必須選擇答案(Must select another answer)。<br />\n<br />\n除了發現新生註冊時被要求填亞裔細分的表格外，<span style=\"color: red;\">有的家長還發現，在沒有得到他們的許可下，學區最近更新的系統中，華裔學生的檔案上會顯示「Chinese」而非「Asian」，引起華裔家長的不滿，更有家長發起抗議行動，要求當局別將亞裔細分。</span>"},{"pid":"c6194a01c69c05160dff3c12e7657cb9befd1f1a","tid":150142,"uid":48210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T20:31:15.000Z","msg":"冇人想認做中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793e0c8423a644cc9f26475b2690cde50b22dff9","tid":150142,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T20:32:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇人想認做中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d40f63a5752e6dfc3667de21ac6e4191b75934","tid":150142,"uid":80913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T20:46:39.000Z","msg":"香港人被標籤為支那人既icon更明顯化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c295863934dcdfefc69c7aea1de81af7e74804a6","tid":150142,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T20: